left class=m><span class=title> Halt!</span><hr size=1> ***Just from behind Madmartigan 10 guards of Mt. Olympus stand there behind him, all dressed in leather, silver armor (lower ranked soldier), a sword, sheild, and spear. And all of the weaponry seemed to be pointed at Madmartigan.*** &quot;Halt! Who goes there!&quot; ***said the largest soldier who was the squad commander.*** <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=madmartigan>Madmartigan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 141<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(8/9/01 12:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=119.topic&index=43>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Halt!</span><hr size=1> ::In a blink, Madmartigan's hand was on his sword's hilt and he was facing the man who spoke to him.::<br>
<br>
&quot;My name...&quot; ::He said roughly, angry for the strange men intruding on his thoughts:: &quot;is Madmartigan. Who i am may be a totaly different story depending on how you act.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Mt Olympus Soldiers</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#FFFF33>(8/9/01 12:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=119.topic&index=44>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> sorry</span><hr size=1> &quot;Madmartigan?...&quot; ***The commanding puts his sword make in its sheth, and gives a grin.*** &quot;Madmartigan as in the warrior, trickster, and over all man of many talents? Well I figure you'd have to be the one if you were here. My Name is Pasilon, commander of this sqaud... You are sort of a role model to us soldiers, we have heard many tales about of you, I welcome you to Mt. Olympus!&quot;  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=madmartigan>Madmartigan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 144<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(8/9/01 1:01 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=119.topic&index=45>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: sorry</span><hr size=1> ::He stares at the solders for a minute then shakes his head an sighs::<br>
<br>
&quot;You dont want me as a rolemodel, trust me. Your boss may not like it. Follow Ares, he's a good rolemodel for solder drones such as yourself. Me, i'm too much of a free spirit.&quot;<br>
<br>
::He straitens up and smiles::<br>
<br>
&quot;Anyway, i want to get up this mountain, so if you'll excuse me...&quot;<br>
<br>
::Madmartigan turns around and starts to climb up the side of the mountain:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Pasilon</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#FFFF33>(8/9/01 1:09 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=119.topic&index=46>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> easy way</span><hr size=1> &quot;Believe me Madmartigan, we olny admire what we want to... No hard feelings? Oh and there is a easier way to get up the mountain.&quot; ***He takes out a dimond which seemed to have a small storm occuring within it if the eye looked close enough, and then he held it in his hand as it started to glow as a large came storming down the side of the mountain and just before it came to Madmartigan and the soldiers in all its rage and power it stopped suddenly and the clouds turned white and a staircase formed.*** &quot;This way...&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=madmartigan>Madmartigan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 145<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(8/9/01 1:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=119.topic&index=47>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: easy way</span><hr size=1> ::Madmartigan chuckled and looked to Pasilon.::<br>
